OOC: Well, i cant speak for everyone else, but i do not agree with you 
kramsey.  I find it fun reading a ton of messages. Soulstice, the last time i 
posted with Vulois was before my Vermont vacation. You probably replied, but 
i didnt get it. We'll just say that Vulois asked him to join him in his quest 
for peace, that ok?

:::Wheeljack/Cyclonus/Scourge/Time Warp:::

::He gives Composer the Datapad::
Wheeljack: First we have to set down the foundation.  After that we can start 
the main structure.  Then some doors--on both sides, because the battle 
location could vary.
~~~~~
::Cyclonus and Scourge reach the base, and shortly after they go in, they 
hear Motormaster's transmission::
Scourge: Unfortunate?
Cyclonus: What could it be?
Scourge: hmmmmm
::Scourge's eyes narrow and Cyclonus gets the hint. He has an angry look now 
as well and clenches his fist::
Cyclonus: Autobots...
~~~~~
::Time Warp sees all of the Radicons outside and hears them talking::
Time Warp: Airbomber, what in the pit's going on?

--part1_105.5bfb4b.27e4de09_boundary
